  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      DES-OSA and P-SAP scores have been validated to detect OSA (Obstructive Sleep Apnea).

      One item of P-SAP and DES-OSA is the measurement of neck circumference. The aim of this study
      is to compare the influence of different methods of neck circumference measurement in the
      accuracy of DES-OSA and P-SAP scores to detect OSA.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
